FIELD is a field to export.

TYPES is a list of strings corresponding to BibTeX entry types
for which the FIELD should be set.  If it is nil, set the FIELD
for all entry types."
  :type '(repeat (string :tag "Field"))
  :group 'org-pdf-scrapper)

